r over a wide wavelength range. With this dust model, the geometric\nparameters are estimated as follows: the inner and outer radii are 30 AU and\n1000 AU and the torus mass is 3.0 M_sun. Assuming an expansion velocity of 15\nkms^{-1}, the torus formation time and mass-loss rate are found to be \\sim300\nyrs and \\sim10^{-2}M_sun yr^{-1} respectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Jan 2013 09:12:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-12"}
