In particular, a solution for a\n60\\,mm(^2) photo sensor with hollow cone is compared to a 36\\,mm(^2) with solid\ncone.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Jan 2013 14:30:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-04-08"}
